Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.06,0:00:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於見到您了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再放走你啦  明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真的來了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起逛倫敦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.29,0:00:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來涅吉弟弟你們打算去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要一起去涅吉弟弟故鄉的村莊喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能說的啊  木乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老師的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老師的故鄉？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…我能不能一起去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.34,0:00:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.46,0:00:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你故鄉裡不是有一大幫魔法使的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.66,0:00:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:00:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的哦  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:01:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶大家來也沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經得到梅爾帝亞納校長的許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥基涅斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}威爾斯  潘布魯克州
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.92,0:01:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是涅吉老師的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉  回到久別的故鄉有何感想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…明明離開這裡才沒有多久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻感覺已經是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得不怎麼真實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.07,0:01:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是  經歷了很多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的經歷了好多好多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  反了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常是反過來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐過得好嗎  有沒有生病
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉你才是  有沒有好好吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.53,0:02:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  姐姐  我給你介紹下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的朋友也是我的學生們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  有好多人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還不是所有人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個美人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和預料中一樣是個美人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們那麼多人打擾貴府
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還讓你們招待了一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這裡的飯真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼美麗的姐姐真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到這位姐姐  也就明白為什麼涅吉那麼彬彬有禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  不過我算放下心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼多活潑可愛的人們支持著你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也請多關照我家的涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會兒我有話想對你說…有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}「毀滅!?涅吉小組!!」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}梅爾帝亞納魔法學校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你要去魔法之國？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了尋找父親的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你才十歲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往魔法世界的大門並不是那麼輕易就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫他的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見  我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古人云「士別三日當刮目相看」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真讓我刮目相看了  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:06:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  這一天比想像中要來得更早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好用你的雙眼看清事實的覺悟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個事件之後  你村子裡的人們都被搬來這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯丹爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我  我是涅吉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那天起已經過了六年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您還是和那時一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時  如果不是斯丹爺爺和姐姐救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定也會和村裡的人們一樣變成石頭放在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會遇到明日菜還有3-A的大家啊  斯丹爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔  斯丹爺爺  你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經長得那麼大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你們  我現在才能在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  路上小心  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞和各位也多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啦  蒔繪  班長  我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼「對不起」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長  你為什麼會在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  這是…那個…不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你不會打算跟來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老師所到之處
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論水深火熱還是天涯海角…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你以為我會這麼說嗎  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會遵守約定的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不能跟你們一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是明日菜同學  如果你讓涅吉老師受到絲毫傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會放過你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我傷痕累累  也會把他平安帶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼能受傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要我怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是所有人都毫髮無傷地回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  這趟旅行應該比想像中要安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這樣就好了  我有種不好的預感…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的預感從來沒可能中過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同學  你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  班長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我會把一切都告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:08:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會不抱什麼期望地等著你的消息的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路走好  涅吉老師  明日菜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都穿好旅館裡發的長袍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟我來吧  小心不要走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  多涅特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你逃走的哦  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把旅館裡的袍子帶來果然是對的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  跟著他們走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gate  通往異世界的大門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這扇門的那一側
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是父親曾經戰鬥並活躍過的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  出發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去向魔法世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去父親的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都等不及了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  讓人好等呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面發光了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼回事  沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙  這可不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位  快撤！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.35,0:11:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以在辦完入境手續之前觀賞城鎮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼涅吉老師也請先去收取手杖還有行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去稍微問下周圍的人看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:11:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手杖  刀劍之類的武器都放在這個封印盒中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是很強力的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在離開Gate Port之前是無法解除的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gate發現偷渡者了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉弟弟！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒔繪同學  你們究竟怎麼過來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明約好了的  抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為怎麼都想跟過來看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  究竟發生了什麼事我們完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡究竟是哪？怎麼搞的這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要露餡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對  這都是我的失職啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們是怎麼過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像事情變得複雜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老師  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個感覺怎麼可能忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但既然蒔繪同學她們能進來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼還有其他人侵入進來也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管多嚴的警備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生事故或者事件的例子  在現實世界也是有過的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再使用一下探知術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警衛員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡負責警備的有幾個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請盡可能都叫過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.41,0:14:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…但是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古老師  明日菜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到這裡來保護蒔繪她們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓同學  麥基涅斯小姐去入境管理局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎去陽台跟著和香她們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攜帶魔杖還在身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起盡全力展開魔法屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉你究竟在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.57,0:14:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這裡使用魔法可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是我想多了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候大家只要笑笑就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然應該不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這也算是血統帶來的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就作為問候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\fsp12}　 {\fsp-2}ΔΟΡΥ　ΠΕΤΡΑΣ{\r}\N這是「石之矛」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是致命傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  不會錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是修學旅行那時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古  快把木乃香大小姐帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉  怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  刹那同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉  涅吉  堅持住！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:15:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？拍電影？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜逼真的演技？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…是嚇唬人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  堅持住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老師的傷危及生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要大小姐的魔法道具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是小刹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的契約卡都交給老師了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超過三分鐘的話就會變得沒辦法用我的力量治好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個盒子  沒有什麼辦法能打開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的  理論上使用了不管用什麼法術都無法解開的方式進行封印的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就會有人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的治癒術法師也會來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子會得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快點叫他們來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  明日菜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉  不行啊  別說話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警衛員！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉·斯普林菲爾德和你的各位同伴們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是稍微下手重了點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過被我一擊就成這個樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是沒有什麼比半吊子的實力還要難看了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不這麼覺得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Fate Averruncus{\r}\N菲特·亞維路克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-5}Μελαν　Και　Σφαιρικον　Δεδμωτηριον
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月見乃夜櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓  小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什麼目的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟蹤我們來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟蹤？別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你們在這裡相遇純屬偶然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次跟你們沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒關係還做這種事！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當自己是誰啊  你們這幫傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個悲劇的事故啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到涅吉他竟然會注意到我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…既然被發現了那就沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總不能讓他叫增援來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便再說一句
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有任何人來救你們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡現在完全與外部隔離了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊  無計可施
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老師的傷現在也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在絕對已經過了兩分鐘以上  沒有武器我什麼也沒法做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這些同伴  對於我來說就是不值一提宛如垃圾般的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在還沒想到一定要抹消這幫人的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也沒有不要這麼做的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用我的永久石化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們全員都退出舞台好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  櫻咲刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你那麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來做你的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…會死的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是死了會讓我也很困擾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且連武器都沒有你要怎麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊？不是打得開的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木乃香！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Adeat{\r}\N阿德阿特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:21:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？剛剛的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.77,0:22:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切…又是麻煩事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.08,0:22:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？事故？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個白髮少年是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的…血？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.76,0:22:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老師受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去給涅吉治傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.51,0:22:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計剩下的時間已經沒30秒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.21,0:22:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.58,0:22:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼重的傷  如果不靠近到能夠接觸到的距離的話是治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.27,0:22:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古菲  支援我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.57,0:22:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.40,0:22:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了  小公主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.93,0:22:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\fsp-2}ΠΝΟΗ　ΠΕΤΡΑΣ{\r}\N石之氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.67,0:22:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你休想碰大小姐一根指頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.95,0:23:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.30,0:23:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匕首·十六串呂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻影？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.02,0:23:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.70,0:23:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…果然沒這麼容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.43,0:23:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.98,0:23:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.56,0:23:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐！注意上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.85,0:23:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.49,0:23:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我  快點幫涅吉治療
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來會會你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.90,0:24:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也被養得…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當可口了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.02,0:24:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.22,0:24:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.85,0:24:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？犬上小太郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.93,0:24:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮絲和咒符？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.02,0:24:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎  你不是被打敗了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.37,0:24:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  差一點就沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說涅吉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.47,0:24:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.44,0:24:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫你施回復咒文你還沒道謝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.27,0:24:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被打敗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.05,0:24:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一點就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.34,0:24:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝居兮高天之原  下告兮禦詔尊存
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.82,0:24:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所遵兮神漏岐命  所囑兮神漏彌尊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.10,0:24:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上敬兮宗祖諸神  畏畏白兮謹聞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.93,0:24:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾有兮嘉友  集侍兮御前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.97,0:25:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肇賜兮加護  重之兮福延
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.71,0:25:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾乃藤原之朝臣  近衛木乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.39,0:25:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬奉兮吾魂  惟眾神兮歆享
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.91,0:25:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍贄兮悉備  謹告兮拜聞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.30,0:25:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木乃香同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.83,0:25:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.49,0:25:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了  涅吉弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.23,0:25:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.69,0:25:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.49,0:25:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  我們反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.18,0:25:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.93,0:25:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.00,0:25:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你不會被打倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.96,0:25:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.09,0:25:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.19,0:25:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.69,0:25:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前說你的同伴是垃圾的發言我現在收回
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.83,0:25:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們究竟是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.24,0:25:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.63,0:26:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾差不多到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.28,0:26:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次就在這裡說再會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.62,0:26:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.64,0:26:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你現在想做什麼  我都會阻止你的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.76,0:26:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都那副樣子了  要怎麼辦到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.87,0:26:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.89,0:26:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-5}висю　тал　ли　сютал　вангэит
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.91,0:26:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\fsp-2}ω，Ταρταρω　κειμενον　βασιλειον　νεκρων{\r}\N噢  沉睡於地底的死者之宮殿
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.19,0:26:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目的已經達成了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.80,0:26:43.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\fsp-2}Ο　ΜΟΝΟΛΙΘΟΣ　ΚΙΩΝ　ΤΟΥ　ΑΙΔΟΥ{\r}\N冥府石柱
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.75,0:26:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.49,0:27:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.27,0:27:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楔的破壞完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.11,0:27:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫離用Gate確保
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.87,0:27:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.22,0:27:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.01,0:27:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趕緊溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.90,0:27:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強制轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.39,0:27:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們分散到世界的盡頭去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.65,0:27:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.38,0:27:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.61,0:27:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得要來這個世界的話  還顯得有點太嫩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.87,0:27:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來你所面對的現實  就算是我送給你的一份禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.83,0:27:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.02,0:27:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥  這個是強制轉移魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.76,0:27:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.91,0:27:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幫傢伙  把Gate的要石給…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.42,0:27:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把世界之間的楔給破壞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.22,0:27:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計連接門的魔力要失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.45,0:28:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家集中起來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.34,0:28:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉住彼此的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.58,0:28:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.44,0:28:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同學！
